# Workspace shape: single-repo cloud checkouts cannot see sibling repos, and
# ephemeral VMs should not accumulate large intermediates.

Capability fs.disk-headroom
  Description At least 1GB of free disk at the project directory
  Probe disk 1024
  Remediation Clean build artifacts or delegate disk-heavy work (media renders, large clones) to a roomier environment.
  Risk low
  Environments local cloud ci

Capability env.claude-code
  Description Running inside a Claude Code session (entrypoint signal present)
  Probe env CLAUDECODE
  Probe env CLAUDE_CODE_ENTRYPOINT
  Remediation Informational only.
  Risk low
  Environments local cloud ci
